&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Help coordinate staff breaks for all Team Members under your supervision&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Work closely with Supervisor, Captain, Parking/Events management, and other stadium staff to resolve customer issues and concerns in a timely and efficient manner&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
